text: Nidal Ali Abu Dukhan () is a Palestinian military officer of the rank of Major General and commander of the Palestinian National Security Forces. He was born in Algeria in 1968. He is married and is the father of two children. He holds a Bachelor degree in Military science from the Cherchell college in Algeria. He was formerly the Commander of Rapid Intervention and Special Operations in the Presidential Guard.سيرته الذاتية على موقع قوات الأمن الوطني الفلسطيني , تاريخ الوصول 22 مارس 2013 On 8 August 2022, the Palestinian president reconstituted the Board of Trustees of Al-Istiqlal University (), and appointed Dhakhan a member of it. == References ==
